FROM LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVIFY1657807054470_shipper_rate_date_extended AS shipper_rate_date_extended
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV3901657807054854_shipper_rate_date_extended_agg AS shipper_rate_date_extended_agg ON shipper_rate_date_extended.date_skey = shipper_rate_date_extended_agg.date_skey
